                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "warn",
                    "source": "Using the user object as returned from supabase.auth.getSession() or from some supabase.auth.onAuthStateChange() events could be insecure! This value comes directly from the storage medium (usually cookies on the server) and many not be authentic. Use supabase.auth.getUser() instead which authenticates the data by contacting the Supabase Auth server.",
                    "target": "使用由 supabase.auth.getSession() 返回的 user 对象或来自某些 supabase.auth.onAuthStateChange() 事件的 user 对象可能不安全！该值直接来自存储介质（通常是服务器上的 cookies），可能不真实。请改用 supabase.auth.getUser()，它会通过联系 Supabase Auth 服务器来验证数据。"
